OL,3,CBrothers jailed after rioting outside
OL,4,CRotherham asylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FTwo brothers have each been jailed for
OL,7,Fthree years for their part in rioting
OL,8,Foutside a hotel housing asylum seekers.
OL,10,FScott and Jason McGuire were part of
OL,11,Fthe disorder which engulfed the
OL,12,FHoliday Inn Express near Rotherham, on
OL,13,FAugust 4 2024, Sheffield Crown Court
OL,14,Fheard on Monday.
OL,16,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC outlined
OL,17,Fhow the McGuire brothers were at the
OL,18,Fforefront of the "mob" during the most
OL,19,Fserious part of the disorder on that
OL,20,FSunday afternoon.
