OL,6,FPolice officers and the hotel itself
OL,7,Fwere pelted with missiles as more than
OL,8,F200 asylum seekers and 22 staff were
OL,9,Ftrapped inside.
OL,11,FAt one point, the rioters smashed
OL,12,Ftheir way into the building and a
OL,13,Fburning wheelie-bin was pushed against
OL,14,Fa fire door.
