OL,6,FA total of 64 officers were injured in
OL,7,Fthe violence along with police horses
OL,8,Fand a dog.Judge Richardson said it was
OL,9,Fhis "misfortune" to have sentenced
OL,10,Fmost of those arrested after the
OL,11,Fdisorder and said he was very familiar
OL,12,Fwith video footage of the violence
OL,13,Fshown in court.
OL,15,FJudge Richardson described how Scott
OL,16,FMcGuire was captured arriving at the
OL,17,Fscene with what appeared to be his
OL,18,Fpartner and a child in a pushchair.
