OL,6,FHe was later pictured in the mob at
OL,7,Fvarious times during the disorder and
OL,8,Fis seen dismantling safety barriers in
OL,9,Ffront of the riot police as well as
OL,10,Fkicking items which were then thrown
OL,11,Fat the officers by others.
OL,13,FThe judge said: "You were involved in
OL,14,Ffierce attacks on police officers
OL,15,Fclose to the hotel.
OL,17,F"You were well to the fore and your
OL,18,Fparticipation was of a high order."
