OL,4,CRotherham asylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FJudge Richardson said Jason McGuire
OL,7,Fwas filmed throwing missiles at
OL,8,Fofficers and a police van as well as
OL,9,Fat the hotel building, while wearing a
OL,10,Fmask.
OL,12,FHe was also filmed tearing down
OL,13,Ffencing which was used by others to
OL,14,Fthrow at the police lines and fuel the
OL,15,Ffire which was set outside the
OL,16,Fbuilding.
OL,18,FThe judge said: "Your involvement was
OL,19,Fwell to the fore in the most serious
OL,20,Faspects of the episodes that
OL,21,Fafternoon."
