OL,4,CRotherham asylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FThe court heard how Jason McGuire was
OL,7,Fjailed for four years in 2015 for a
OL,8,Fdrugs offence and for 10 years in 2018
OL,9,Ffor a machete attack.
OL,11,FThe brothers were jailed on Monday at
OL,12,FSheffield Crown Court along with two
OL,13,Fothers men, Keethan Reeve-Lawson and
OL,14,FDaniel Kazemi.
OL,16,FThis is understood to have brought the
OL,17,Ftotal number of people sentenced for
OL,18,Fthe Rotherham violence to 104.
