OL,3,CBrothers jailed after rioting outside
OL,4,CRotherham asylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FThe judge has heard over dozens of
OL,7,Fhearings how the hotel was besieged
OL,8,Ffor around 12 hours.
OL,10,FHe said: "Each time I see this
OL,11,Fexceptionally serious disturbance
OL,12,Frepresented in the footage of these
OL,13,Fevents I feel, as I'm sure many others
OL,14,Ffeel, profound shame that such
OL,15,Fshocking disorder should occur in this
OL,16,Fcountry."
