OL,3,CBrothers jailed after rioting outside
OL,4,CRotherham asylum seeker hotel
OL,6,FThe judge said: "The venom of racism
OL,7,Fand racially motivated violence
OL,8,Fsuffuses the events from first to
OL,9,Flast."Judge Richardson told the
OL,10,Fdefendants: "Several hundred people
OL,11,Fwere intent on mob rule.
OL,13,FThat will never be tolerated in this
OL,14,Fcountry."
OL,16,FJudge Richardson jailed Reeve-Lawson
OL,17,Fand Kazemi for 22 months each after
OL,18,Fhearing how they were involved in
OL,19,Flater incidents once police had
OL,20,Fmanaged to push the mob away from
OL,21,Fimmediately outside the hotel.
