OL,6,FKazemi was filmed throwing a can of
OL,7,Fbeer at officers, which smashed
OL,8,Fagainst their shields, and the judge
OL,9,Fnoted that he was "visibly happy" when
OL,10,Fanother man threw a metal bar at
OL,11,Fpolice.
OL,13,FRichard Barradell, defending Kazemi,
OL,14,Fsaid "like many others" his client
OL,15,Fjoined in "once the pack mentality
OL,16,Fstarted".He said: "He cannot for the
OL,17,Flife of him explain why."
OL,19,FMr Barradell said his client was
OL,20,F"bitterly embarrassed" and wanted to
OL,21,Fapologise to everyone involved.
